- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with optimizing the spread of information among agents (users). 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a less likely category but possible as the paper proposes an algorithm for optimizing a marketing campaign.
